title: Cai Cai Tou
synopsis: Caicaitou CAICAITOON was born in September 2005 as a naughty and cute child who interprets the colorful childhood story. Sometimes humorous and sometimes calm and calm. Funny FLASH stories and funny chat emoticons are popular among netizens. CAICAITOON's great ideal is to be a protector of the earth's environment. In his village, there are many friends, the lovely sister "Cauliflower", the portable partner "Garlic Garlic", and the enemy's little rival "Dangdantou". They live together in a green and peaceful world. (translated form iqiyi)
